-- Balda Slumps 20% After Lowering Forecast, Saying Company Like to Post Loss
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2010-10-15T07:09:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-15/balda-slumps-20-after-lowering-forecast-saying-company-like-to-post-loss.html
Balda AG fell the most since
December 2008 in Frankfurt trading after lowering its 2010
forecast and saying earnings before interest and taxes are
likely to be “negative in the single-digit range.”  The shares sank 20 percent to 5.40 euros as of 9:08 a.m.
local time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Julie Cruz at 
 jcruz6@bloomberg.net  